Phase 13 (continued): Maintenance - Part 3
Monthly Tasks
1. Review Case Completion Rates:  
SQL:  
```
SELECT 
    c.case_label,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ur.user_id) as attempted_users,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ur.is_completed THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as completed_count
FROM cases c
LEFT JOIN user_responses ur ON c.case_id = ur.case_id
GROUP BY c.case_id, c.case_label
ORDER BY attempted_users DESC;
```
2. Update Email Configuration if SMTP credentials expire
3. Archive Old Data if needed:
SQL
```
-- Archive completed responses older than 1 year
CREATE TABLE user_responses_archive LIKE user_responses;
INSERT INTO user_responses_archive 
SELECT * FROM user_responses 
WHERE is_completed = TRUE AND completed_at < DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 YEAR);
```